panels/lighthouse/LighthouseController.t.message: Ingahlola kuphela amakhasi ku-HTTP noma ku-HTTPS. Funa ekhasini elehlukile.
Ingabe leli khasi lilandela imikhuba ehamba phambili yini yokuthuthukiswa kwewebhu kwesimanje
Ingabe leli khasi liyahlangabezana nezinga Uhlelo Lokusebenza Lewebhu Eliqhubekayo
Lolu hlelo lokusebenza luthatha isikhathi esingakanani ukubonisa okuqukethwe bese luyasebenziseka
Ingabe leli khasi lilungiselelwe izinga lesikhangiso nekhwalithi
Ingabe leli khasi lenzelwe izinga lemiphumela yenjini yokusesha
Ingabe leli khasi lingasetshenziswa abantu abakhubazekile
I-JavaScript ikhutshaziwe. Kudingeka unike i-JavaScript amandla ukuze uhlaziye leli khasi. Vula Imenyu Yomyalo bese uqalisa umyalo Wokunika Amandla i-JavaScript ukuze unike amandla i-JavaScript.
Amathebhu amaningi alawulwa nge-service worker efanayo. Vala amanaye amathebhu wakho kokoqobo okufanayo ukuhlola leli khasi.
Imodi yokuzulazula ihlaziya ukulayishwa kwekhasi, njengemibiko engokoqobo ye-Lighthouse.
Setha kabusha isitoreji (cache, service workers, njll) ngaphambi koku-oditha. (Ilungele ukusebenza kanye nokuhlola kwe-PWA)
Qalisa i-Lighthouse ngokuzulazula, ubude besikhathi, noma imodi yesifinyezo

I-throttling elingisiwe ilingisa ukulayisha ikhasi ngokulengayo ngokuselwe kudatha evela ekulayisheni kwasekuqaleni okungenziwanga i-throttle. Ukwenza i-throttling i-DevTools kwenza ukuthi ikhasi lilenge.
Imodi yesifinyezo ihlaziya ikhasi esimweni esithile, ngokuvamile ngemva kokusebenzelana komsebenzisi.
Kungase kube khona idatha egciniwe ethinta ukusebenza kokulayisha kulezi zindawo: {PH1}. Hlola leli khasi kwiwindi le-incognito ukugwema lezo zinsiza ekuthinteni imiphumela yakho.
Kungahle kube nedatha elondoloziwe ethinta ukusebenza kokulayisha kule ndawo: {PH1}. Ukuhlola leli khasi kukuwinid le-incognito ukuvimbela lezo zinsiza ukuthinta imiphumela yakho.
Imodi ye-timespan ihlaziya isikhathi esinqunyiwe, ngokuvamile esiqukethe ukusebenzisana komsebenzisi.
